{
    "Email_Body": "Hi Informatica Support, I have an issue",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Hello"
}

{
   "Email_Body": "I would like to request adding an email listener feature to the CAI platform. This feature would allow the system to automatically monitor incoming emails and process them, triggering workflows or responses without any manual steps. Having this functionality would help us streamline how we handle email communications and improve response times. ",
   "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
   "Email_Subject": "Email Listener for CAI"
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Dear Informatica Support, We’ve appreciated the recent performance enhancements, but during high traffic periods, IDMC sync jobs occasionally slow down noticeably. This affects our daily operations. Monitoring this and optimizing performance further would greatly benefit users relying on peak time processing. Thanks for listening to our feedback. Kind regards, Piotr Wójcik ",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Feedback on Performance During Peak Hours "
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Informatica Support,We’ve been dealing with repeated sync failures in IDMC, and frankly, this is becoming unacceptable. Every time we schedule a data sync, something breaks—records fail to update or the jobs just stall with no clear error messages. We’ve wasted a lot of time trying to troubleshoot on our own, only to see the same problems again and again. We expect a prompt and thorough investigation because these ongoing issues are severely impacting our business operations. Please provide a solution immediately instead of generic responses. Awaiting your urgent response. James Wilson",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Continuous IDMC Sync Failures"
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Hello, After a failed attempt to upgrade the Informatica agent, I'm unable to restart it using AgentManager. Is there an alternative way to start the agent if AgentManager isn't working properly?",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Unable to restart agent after failed upgrade"
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Thank you for reaching out to us.This message is a response to your Zendesk ticket number: 60 . We have created a response to your inquiry below.Please find your original question and our answer for your reference. If you have any further questions, feel free to contact us again. If you do not have any further questions, please mark the ticket as solved Your inquiry:Subject: Unable to restart agent after failed upgrade Hello, After a failed attempt to upgrade the Informatica agent, I'm unable to restart it using AgentManager. Is there an alternative way to start the agent if AgentManager isn't working properly?Our response:Yes, you can start the agent from Services or by running the runagent.bat file from the command prompt as an administrator.",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Unable to restart agent after failed upgrade"
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Please provide more details.-----Original Message-----From: nearshoreaidevelopment@gmail.com <nearshoreaidevelopment@gmail.com> Sent: Friday, August 29, 2025 1:23 PMTo: Kucharska,Kamila <kkucharska@informatica.com>Subject: Response to Your Support RequestCaution: This email originated from outside of the organization. Review for Phishing!Thank you for reaching out to us.This message is a response to your Zendesk ticket number: 60 We have created a response to your inquiry below.Please find your original question and our answer for your reference.If you have any further questions, feel free to contact us again. If you do not have any further questions, please mark the ticket as solvedYour inquiry:Subject: Unable to restart agent after failed upgrade Hello, After a failed attempt to upgrade the Informatica agent, I'm unable to restart it using AgentManager. Is there an alternative way to start the agent if AgentManager isn't working properly?Our response:Yes, you can start the agent from Services or by running the runagent.bat file from the command prompt as an administrator.",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Unable to restart agent after failed upgrade"
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Hi Informatica Support Team, I would like to request access to the feature that allows exporting sync job history and logs from IDMC. This capability is essential for our auditing and reporting processes. Could you please enable this access for our account or let me know the steps required to do so? Thank you for your assistance. Best regards, Adam Smith ",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "Request for Access to Export Sync Job History in IDMC  "
}

{
    "Email_Body": "Here is the information.We’ve been dealing with repeated sync failures in IDMC, and frankly, this is becoming unacceptable. Every time we schedule a data sync, something breaks—records fail to update or the jobs just stall with no clear error messages. We’ve wasted a lot of time trying to troubleshoot on our own, only to see the same problems again and again. We expect a prompt and thorough investigation because these ongoing issues are severely impacting our business operations. Please provide a solution immediately instead of generic responses. Awaiting your urgent response. James Wilson",
    "Email_Address": "kkucharska@informatica.com",
    "Email_Subject": "RE: Request for Additional Information 57"
}
